dct_title_s: The Balkans. Turkey, scale 1:250.000: Mt. Athos. Series G.S.G.S. no. 2097 [cartographic material].
dct_description_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 2097. North Decimal Degree 40.5833. South Decimal Degree 39.7500. East Decimal Degree 24.3333. West Decimal Degree 22.6667. Alternate title: The Balkans: Mt. Athos. Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. Glossary of terms in Turkish and English. Map is part of a set of 23 sheets. For holdings see index.
